        "row_3bqNPx": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "caption": "ABOUT",
            "heading": "Why Outexer",
            "text": "<p>At Outexer, we believe that true health is hidden in our daily home life. We draw on the wisdom of traditional saunas and carefully polish each product to bring you the ultimate and deep health experience. We perfectly combine dedicated craftsmanship with cutting-edge far-infrared technology - the design is minimalist and neat, and the heating is warm and comfortable. Every detail is just to make you more relaxed, healthier and more balanced.<br/><br/>We select materials and strive for the ultimate, just for safety. All sauna materials (Canadian Hemlock or Okoume wood) are hand-selected and rigorously tested, and our far-infrared saunas are equipped with low-EMF graphene heating panels. Whether you want to choose a single, multi-person, indoor or outdoor sauna, you can trust Outexer. We put your safety first and create a trustworthy resting place for your home health.<br/><br/><strong>Trustworthy Quality | Safer Sauna | Better Health</strong></p>",
            "button_label": "Learn More",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/about-us"
          }
        }
